beta2 methods

beta2 returns a vector with all the estimated values of the \(d_i = \beta1 u_i + \beta2 w_i + \epsilon_i\) models fitted by ChIPexoQual

beta2(object)

# S4 method for ExoData
beta2(object)

Arguments

object
a ExoData object.

Value

A numeric vector with estimated values for \(\beta_2\).

Examples

data(exoExample)
